Remote Utilities (Viewer + Host) 6.3.0.2 Multilingual 

Remote Utilities is a program designed to provide remote administration options for computers as part of local or wide area networks. Remote Utilities consists of two components: 

RUT-Server is the part that is installed on the remote computer (it is possible to install it remotely) 

RUT-Viewer which is the part installed on the administrators computer. You can use it to control remote computers.
